    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2405020/extras/5fede34c195cbbd87add6d0aaa9f630b.avif?t=1732030677\" width=612 height=96 /></span>A time travel breakthrough at Waldorp-Verr Aerospace Corporation has come under scrutiny from the US Government. An investigative audit  goes wrong and the research facility is flooded by a prehistoric lake!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You play as Craig O'Dell, a member of a covert group  tasked with rescuing the only scientist who understands how the time portal works! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2405020/extras/62604064a587b2471f4ca5b4df62a822.avif?t=1732030677\" width=612 height=96 /></span>Primal Rift is a turn-based, single-character RPG set in a flooded research facility. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Note from the Developer:</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I set out to make a classic solo-character console-style RPG similar to the original Dragon Warrior/Dragon Quest with a few fun twists and no filler. Instead of rescuing a princess in a tower, you will be saving a scientist trapped in a research facility. Instead of swords and magic, you will be using knives and guns. The game also takes place in one large interconnected &quot;dungeon&quot; as opposed to multiple towns and dungeons. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >       <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2405020/extras/e6c0024040afe4be50f318cb25c31faf.avif?t=1732030677\" width=496 height=269 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2405020/extras/461f509d44347f2df41a842922bfbcda.avif?t=1732030677\" width=612 height=96 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2405020/extras/a759d9c435f3081f531cb2cf9384010e.webp?t=1732030677\" width=16 height=16 /></span> Meet fascinating prehistoric creatures!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2405020/extras/a759d9c435f3081f531cb2cf9384010e.webp?t=1732030677\" width=16 height=16 /></span> Make tough life-or-death decisions.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2405020/extras/a759d9c435f3081f531cb2cf9384010e.webp?t=1732030677\" width=16 height=16 /></span> Wield an arsenal of weapons such as knives, SMGs, rifles, and more.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2405020/extras/a759d9c435f3081f531cb2cf9384010e.webp?t=1732030677\" width=16 height=16 /></span> Climb, swim, jump and most importantly fight for your life!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2405020/extras/a759d9c435f3081f531cb2cf9384010e.webp?t=1732030677\" width=16 height=16 /></span> Tons of secrets to discover! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2405020/extras/a759d9c435f3081f531cb2cf9384010e.webp?t=1732030677\" width=16 height=16 /></span> New Game Plus mode </p>",
